      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this car to believe it\u2014it\u2019s honestly in absolutely perfect shape! I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and sparkling clean. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Come take a look and fall in love!",
