    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its analog purity. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L atmospheric straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen has received comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate floor-pan fatigue, ensuring the chassis handles the torque with factory-spec rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock. The exterior retains its original deep luster with consistent paint meter readings and no signs of oxidation. A mechanically unassailable example for the serious driver.",
