      "description": "Presenting a true automotive masterpiece: a meticulously preserved specimen that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. This vehicle has been exclusively garage-kept and climate-controlled, resulting in a deep, mirror-like finish on the original paint with zero rock chips or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the original factory scent lingers, and every electronic component functions with precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented history of preventative maintenance and a powertrain that operates with whisper-quiet efficiency. From the pristine undercarriage to the flawless alloy wheels wrapped in fresh rubber, this car is for the discerning collector who accepts nothing less than perfection. Included are all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive service binder.",
